{
  "id": "adv_bond_ai_01_03",
  "title": "小美山愛3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～、ここが優ちゃんが京都で\n行きつけだったラーメン屋さんなんですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ so this is Yu-chan's favorite\nramen shop in Kyoto~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.5666669528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "せやで～。地元に戻るたびずーっと店長さんに\n「東京進出してきてほしいな～」ってお願いしててん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right~. Every time I went back to my hometown‚ I'd always beg\nthe manager to 'I wish you'd open a shop in Tokyo‚ too~'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.500000604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらようやく重い腰を上げて\n二号店を東京にオープンしてくれたんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After much persuasion‚\nhe finally opened a second shop in Tokyo",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.500000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4666680336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんの努力が実って今日私達は\nここのラーメンが食べれるんですね……感動です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan's efforts paid off‚ and today\nwe can enjoy this ramen… I'm so touched!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666680336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5333347003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "願いは口に出せば叶うんやな～。はぁ～……\n豚骨スープのええ香り……京都店と全く同じや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wishes have to be spoken~. Haa~…\nWonderful smell of the tonkotsu soup… exactly the same as the Kyoto…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5333347003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2159465472
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2000013669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "くんくん。ラーメン屋さんってラーメンが運ばれてくる\nまでの香りを嗅いで待ってる時間もワクワクしますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sniff sniff. At a ramen shop‚ even the time I wait for the ramen to come out\nand smell it makes my heart race",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2000013669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2333387692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "めっちゃ分かるわ……味を想像するだけで白ご飯\nいけるもん。愛ちゃん、注文はどうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I totally agree… just imagining the taste makes me want to eat\na bowl of rice. Ai-chan‚ what would you like to order?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2333387692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.7666723568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちは『特製混豚黄昏ラーメン』のこってりにさらに\n煮卵とチャーシュートッピングプラスして追い飯！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like the rich flavor of \"Special Mixed Pork Twilight Ramen\"\nplus the boiled egg and charsiu toppings‚ add a bowl of rice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7666723568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.7333390235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ私も優ちゃんと同じので！　初めて来たお店では\n常連さんと同じものを頼むって決めてるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I'll order the same thing as Yu-chan! It's standard to order the same thing\nas a regular when the first visit a restaurant!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333390235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3000056902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいわ～、愛ちゃんにうちの好きなラーメンを\n食べてもらえるなんて！　サイドメニューは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So happy~‚ that Ai-chan is eating\nmy favorite ramen! The side menu is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3000056902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.6666723568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "餃子がめっちゃ美味しいんやけどニンニクが\n強いんよね……でもめっちゃ美味しいねん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dumpling are really good‚ but garlic flavor\nis strong… but it's really good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6666723568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6666723568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "私は今日はオフだし大丈夫です！　優ちゃんも\nオフでしたよね？　せっかくだし頼んじゃいましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm off today‚ so it's fine! Yu-chan is\noff work too‚ right? Since we have this chance‚ let's have fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6666723568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.6333349545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "せやね、うん、頼んじゃいましょ！\nそれなら、ニンニク増し増し餃子にしましょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ right‚ let's have fun!\nIn that case‚ let's make dumplings with lots of garlic added!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333349545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4066032727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ～！　ラーメンが運ばれてきた瞬間ぶわぁって\n凄い濃厚な豚骨スープの香りが……！　美味しそう～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~! The moment the ramen comes out‚\nsmell of the rich and thick tonkotsu soup hit me…! Looks delicious~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333390236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.9666723569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て！　この黄昏色の豚骨スープ！　いつまでも\n眺めてられる……けど、冷める前に、食べましょか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ look! This twilight-colored tonkotsu soup! I could stare\nat it forever… but before it gets cold‚ let's try it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9666723569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9362325986
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0666723569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃあ髪を結んで……\nいただきまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I'll tie my hair up…\nLet's eatー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0666723569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.3204789162
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4438516299
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.34296182
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3333512306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふーふー……、うんまぁい～\nやっぱりラーメンは最高や。どう、愛ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hooー hooー… so good~\nRamen is the best‚ after all. What do you think‚ Ai-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3333512306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.7666794777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "じゅるるる～、ごくん……あぁ～\nこってりスープが麺に絡んでて最高です～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Slurp~ sorry… ahh~\nThe rich soup clings to the noodles‚ it's the best~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7666794777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.6666764259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでもらえて嬉しいわ～。ささっ、こっちの餃子も\n食べてみて！　ニンニクがほんまにいい感じやから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So glad you enjoyed it~ Here here‚ try this\ndumplings! The garlic tastes really good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6666764259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.4000097592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　ぱくっ……！\nはふはふで、おいひ～でふ～。ぱくっ！　ぱくっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here we goー! Crunch…!\nIt's hot~ and delicious~. Crunch! Crunch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4000097592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.818572998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～、美味しかった～。仕事前は匂いつくから\n行かれへんけどまたオフの日に来よな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew~‚ it was good~. We can't come on our work day because it might smell‚\nbut we'll come back on out next day off~",
